at Second City on Thursday. From left are director Peter Torekvei and actors 
Robin Duke, Diane Stilwell, Chris Barnes, Dana Anderson. Behind them is Richard 
Kind, in foreground Ryan Stiles. LARRY DAVIS/Los Angeles Times; Photo, HELLO: 
