<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY DIGEST: HUNTINGTON BEACH; 
</P>
<P>
DRIVER DIES IN CRASH; PASSENGER IS UNHURT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A 23-year-old sailor was killed early Sunday when he lost control of the car he 
was driving on Pacific Coast Highway and crashed into a fence. 
</P>
<P>
Richard A. Frost of Long Beach was killed about 2:20 a.m. when the car struck 
the wood-frame, chain-link fence near Warner Avenue. 
</P>
</TEXT>
