RIGHTS; PROSTITUTION; PARKING VIOLATIONS; LOITERING; TRESPASSING; ARRESTS -- 
ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA071089-0080 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 80484 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 10, 1989, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
