<SUBJECT>
<P>
ALL STAR GAMES; ANAHEIM STADIUM; MAJOR LEAGUE BASEBALL (ORGANIZATION); ANAHEIM 
(CA) -- HISTORY; CALIFORNIA ANGELS (BASEBALL TEAM) 
</P>
